00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:40,920
I wouldn't dare.

498
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:43,460
You bossed around when you assigned work.

499
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:45,600
It scared me, and I'm still shaking.

500
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:47,360
What kind of boss does that?

501
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:49,300
I'll help you deal with him.

502
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:58,560
I thought you were mad because I criticized you like that in public.

503
00:33:58,560 --> 00:34:00,540
Am I that stupid?

504
00:34:00,540 --> 00:34:03,140
I know you are helping me.

505
00:34:03,140 --> 00:34:06,580
And it was indeed the retest that led to the rectification of the paper.

506
00:34:06,580 --> 00:34:09,400
It's normal that people are mad at me.

507
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:15,170
But, the stricter you are with me, the more they'll sympathize with me.

508
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:20,230
Yes, but not exactly.

509
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:21,980
What do you mean?

510
00:34:21,980 --> 00:34:24,720
You really want to criticize me?

511
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:27,150
Let's talk at home.

512
00:34:33,080 --> 00:34:34,720
Eat first, then talk.

513
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:37,300
Talk first, then eat.

514
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:45,880
Wei'an, why do I make you read those articles?

515
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,480
To keep up with all the research developments?

516
00:34:47,480 --> 00:34:48,920
What is our goal?

517
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:53,220
To prove the problem with HDQ39 and its connection with aneurysms.

518
00:34:53,220 --> 00:34:54,160
That's right.

519
00:34:54,160 --> 00:35:01,310
Have you thought about why studies on drugs of the same type with similar mechanisms always fail in Phase III clinical trials?

520
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:08,220
In this situation, rather than all the crowning arguments in the paper,

521
00:35:08,220 --> 00:35:10,960
shouldn't we understand what they are really doing?

522
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:14,700
Shouldn't you learn all the supplementary materials?

523
00:35:14,700 --> 00:35:16,300
I should.

524
00:35:17,140 --> 00:35:19,920
I didn't think this through.

525
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:22,720
Then starting from tonight,

526
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:27,540
let's read through these ten papers together, word by word.

527
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:31,920
Find a breakthrough in the paper to design the experiment.

528
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:33,680
So much work.

529
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:38,920
I shouldn't have fallen in love with the teacher.

530
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:44,180
There are endless review materials and endless tests every day.

531
00:35:44,180 --> 00:35:46,300
What?

532
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:47,960
Are you afraid?

533
00:35:47,960 --> 00:35:51,060
It's too late for regrets now.

534
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:55,000
Do you think other couples are the same as us?

535
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:58,640
Working on their careers day and night?

536
00:36:00,640 --> 00:36:02,920
If you don't want to work,

537
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:05,840
do you want to do something else?

538
00:36:08,820 --> 00:36:10,400
Let's eat.

539
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,920
I'm addicted to my studies.

540
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:16,160
Let's eat.

541
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:18,360
Here, broccoli.

542
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:20,320
Mom!

543
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:22,480
You're back.

544
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:24,260
Why did you call me back so urgently?

545
00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:25,900
Where's Dad?

546
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:29,740
Don't drink that.

547
00:36:29,740 --> 00:36:33,460
This is pear and white wood ear soup I just made. Here you go.

548
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:35,480
You all are so busy.

549
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:37,760
No one can stay by my side.

550
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:39,960
If you have something to say, just say it.

551
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:46,520
I heard that Xiao Ran didn't get the research assistant position she applied for.

552
00:36:46,520 --> 00:36:48,480
She can't stay at the hospital either.

553
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:51,460
How about letting her join Jiehui?

554
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:56,480
Why are you getting involved in the company's operations?

555
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:58,560
I know you two broke up.

556
00:36:58,560 --> 00:37:02,200
And there's a problem with the project Professor Wen is researching.

557
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,680
But Xiao Ran's heart for you has never changed.

558
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:07,600
Besides, your company needs someone like Xiao Ran

559
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:10,000
who knows what's best for you.

560
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:13,280
She can help you solve tough problems.

561
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:16,760
Tough problems?

562
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:23,400
Yuncheng, I told you so.

563
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:28,080
How can we let go of our three-year relationship so easily?

564
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:32,560
Xiao Ran, I heard that

565
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:36,920
you didn't get the research assistant position in the end.

566
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:40,000
Jiehui is in need of a marketing manager right now.

567
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:41,600
Come to the company and help me.

568
00:37:41,600 --> 00:37:48,000
Yuncheng, the reason I interviewed for the research assistant position is that no matter when,

569
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:52,160
as long as you needed me, I can be by your side.

570
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:56,160
I just didn't expect to get set up by Su Wei'an.

571
00:37:56,160 --> 00:38:01,220
When I video-chatted with her back then, I asked her what to do if there are too many false positives after staining.

572
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:03,880
She didn't mention the antibodies at all back then.

573
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:06,460
She set me up on purpose.

574
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:12,040
None of this matters. I know your abilities.

575
00:38:12,040 --> 00:38:16,120
It's just that the company has requirements for performance reviews.

576
00:38:16,120 --> 00:38:19,360
They can't lower the standards just because I introduced you.

577
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:22,220
You can understand, right?

578
00:38:22,220 --> 00:38:23,360
Of course.

579
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:25,600
I don't need any special treatment.

580
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:31,880
As long as I can watch you from a distance at the company, I'll be satisfied.

581
00:38:32,580 --> 00:38:36,980
Yuncheng, I know you loved Su Wei'an in the past.

582
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:40,900
If you see her again, it'll be hard for you to let go.

583
00:38:40,900 --> 00:38:43,780
But she is Gu Yunzheng's girlfriend now.

584
00:38:43,780 --> 00:38:45,960
Can we still...

585
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:47,560
Xiao Ran.

586
00:38:49,060 --> 00:38:52,780
I've put a lot of effort into HDQ39.

587
00:38:52,780 --> 00:38:54,660
You've seen that over the years.

588
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:57,300
Now there's so much negative news surrounding the company.

589
00:38:57,300 --> 00:39:00,620
It's still unclear whether or not this drug can make it to the market.

590
00:39:00,620 --> 00:39:05,000
If it's not handled well,  it will be a fatal blow to Jiehui.

591
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:10,880
So, I'm not in the mood to think about anything else right now.

592
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:27,160

593
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:28,840
The unblinded results show that

594
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:33,740
the three patients who experienced adverse reactions were all taking HDQ39,

595
00:39:33,740 --> 00:39:35,765
and not the placebo.

596
00:39:35,765 --> 00:39:39,040
How do you explain this?

597
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:43,020
Professor, less than 10 percent of the samples were lost.

598
00:39:43,020 --> 00:39:44,940
It will not affect the launch of HDQ39.

599
00:39:44,940 --> 00:39:47,380
We haven't figured out the side effects of this drug yet.

600
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:48,700
Can it be launched so rashly?

601
00:39:48,700 --> 00:39:52,840
As long as the process is in compliance, the launch won't be affected.

602
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:56,340
Prepare materials right now to submit a report to the Ethics Committee.

603
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:58,920
Let them make the decision.

604
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,350
Professor.

605
00:40:01,140 --> 00:40:05,980
The patients experienced adverse events after they withdrew from the trial.

606
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:10,560
We don't have to report it.

607
00:40:13,380 --> 00:40:14,970
Xiao Yang,

608
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:17,860
don't forget we are doctors.

609
00:40:17,860 --> 00:40:22,480
We consider the patient's health as the top priority, not anything else.

610
00:40:22,480 --> 00:40:28,520
I researched HDQ39 to relieve the symptoms of Huntington's disease,

611
00:40:28,520 --> 00:40:31,020
not to pursue profits from it going to market.

612
00:40:31,020 --> 00:40:37,900
You... The way you're talking now doesn't seem like you're a doctor from Zhang He Hospital, but an employee of Jiehui.

613
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,160
- Professor— 
 - Tell me.

614
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:41,740
What benefits did Jiehui Company give you?

615
00:40:41,740 --> 00:40:43,400
Professor!

616
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:50,560
I admit, I am a bit impatient.

617
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:55,570
But that's because I don't want to see our years of hard work go to waste.

618
00:40:56,180 --> 00:41:00,280
There really is no benefit transfer between me and Jiehui.

619
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:06,160
If you don't believe me,

620
00:41:07,180 --> 00:41:09,740
you can ask Miss Wen.

621
00:41:09,740 --> 00:41:14,220
She is an employee of Jiehui now.

622
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:16,620
What did you say?

623
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:25,980

624
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:38,400
Dad, you are back.

625
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:40,000
Old Wen,

626
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,760
