627
00:41:47,940 --> 00:41:53,960
Xiao Ran, why did you join Jiehui without letting us know?

628
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:58,860
I'm not interested in clinical practice.

629
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:00,940
I want to do scientific research.

630
00:42:00,940 --> 00:42:03,420
Yuncheng happens to have a job opening.

631
00:42:03,420 --> 00:42:05,520
Jiehui is also a big company.

632
00:42:05,520 --> 00:42:12,660
Xiao Ran, didn't you say earlier that you were going to apply for the research assistant position at Huaren?

633
00:42:14,140 --> 00:42:17,080
Yes. I considered it.

634
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:20,800
I think Jiehui's pay is better than Huaren's.

635
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:24,400
Are you unwilling to work there, or are you unable to?

636
00:42:27,080 --> 00:42:30,560
I have already figured out the whole story of how you got to Jiehui.

637
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:31,800
Did you know?

638
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:35,720
Your daughter was fired by Huaren.

639
00:42:36,440 --> 00:42:39,280
Xiao Ran, is that true?

640
00:42:39,280 --> 00:42:41,270
What's going on?

641
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:44,900
No, Dad. It was that Su Wei'an.

642
00:42:44,900 --> 00:42:47,400
She just had to compete with me for the research assistant position.

643
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:50,300
She just wanted to prove that there's an issue with HDQ39.

644
00:42:50,300 --> 00:42:51,440
She's up to no good.

